OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Ffine dry and sunny evening. Some clear
OL,7,Fspells at first tonight but turning
OL,8,Fcloudier overnight, with perhaps the
OL,9,Fodd light shower.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FAny cloud breaking up to allow
OL,12,Fsome sunny spells, and becoming warm.
OL,13,FCloud and patchy rain spreading to the
OL,14,FIsles later in afternoon perhaps
OL,15,Freaching far north Highland in evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
