OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FSome
OL,6,Fwarm sunshine on Tuesday but west
OL,7,Fclouding over with patchy rain. The
OL,8,Fwest cloudy on Wednesday, light
OL,9,Fshowers, east brighter, warmer. Some
OL,10,Fwarm sunshine Thursday but chance of
OL,11,Fshowers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
